  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bcb\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bcb\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gas scam like central bank bond scam will be allowed - United People's Power",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "In the current situation where the country is facing a massive economic crisis, the United People's Power Member of Parliament SM Marikar accused the rulers of allowing the importation of gas at high prices and said that they are planning to take appropriate legal action against this scam through the committee soon.",
        "He said the above while attending a press conference organized at the Office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo (06) on Wednesday. There he added:",
        "We had revealed information about the importation of gas at high prices. After that, we had written a request to Saritha Herat, Chairman of the Cob Committee, to look into the matter.",
        "Accordingly, a committee was convened in the Parliament. However, its investigations were a lot of fun for us.",
        "Although there is an opportunity to import goods at lower prices, it is never acceptable for the rulers to allow higher prices to be imported.",
        "We can never allow a gas scam like last time's central bank bond scam to happen.",
        "Therefore, the auditor general's assessment report on the price requests issued by Litro in relation to gas import and subsequent import prices will be submitted in two weeks.",
        "Based on that, we are ready to take legal action through the committee."
      ],
